      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲情報から、このチャンネルでしか見られない\n私達のオフまで、どんどん配信する予定です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2558267196,
      "endTime": 42.9467359146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "kana、こっちでも金の盾ほしいんで！！\n絶対、チャンネル登録してね～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1334024669,
      "endTime": 48.840068745800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
